title: CENTRAL DIVISION WOMEN PREPARE FOR THE EXPO NEXT WEEK (Government of the Republic of Fiji) ...
text: ( Source : Government of the Republic of Fiji ) 10/8/ 2015 The women from the central division are all geared up for Fiji's second National Women 's Expo which will be held at the Vodafone Arena in Suva next week from Wednesday 14th to Friday
